<section id="introduction" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
<p>This dataset looks at 3,282 global chocolate sales from 2022 to 2025. It includes 6 variables per sale:</p>
<table class="caption-top table">
<caption>Variables included in dataset</caption>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Sales Person</td>
<td>Country</td>
<td>Product</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td>Date</td>
<td>Amount</td>
<td>Boxes Shipped</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><a href="https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/saidaminsaidaxmadov/chocolate-sales?resource=download" class="uri">https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/saidaminsaidaxmadov/chocolate-sales?resource=download</a></p>
