</section>
<section id="questions-of-interest" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="questions-of-interest">Questions of Interest:</h2>
<p>What is the average price per box of chocolate in each country?</p>
<p>Which countries are making the most chocolate sales by number of boxes?</p>
<p>Which countries are making the most chocolate sales by amount of money?</p>
</section>
<section id="visualizations" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="visualizations">Visualizations</h2>
