  <description><![CDATA[ 





<section id="introduction" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
<p>This dataset looks at 6,607 students and 19 factors that could possibly contribute to exam score. This includes how much students slept and studied, the access to resources they have (including supportive parents and good teachers) and many other variables.</p>
<table class="caption-top table">
<caption>Variables included in “Student Academic Performance” dataset</caption>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 25%">
<col style="width: 25%">
<col style="width: 25%">
<col style="width: 25%">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
